            <div class='highlight'><pre><code class="language-git">fix(api): fix error in user validation<br><br>The user registration endpoint was allowing registrations with invalid email addresses. An additional validation has been added to ensure that email addresses are valid.<br><br>Closes #456</code></pre></div>
