      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Tools for generating changelogs from conventional commits">Tools for generating changelogs from conventional commits<a class="anchor-link" href="#Tools for generating changelogs from conventional commits"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 29" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
